dct_description_sm: At top of map: Rand-McNally indexed atlas. [South Africa]. 490-491. Map of South Africa, showing portion of German South West Africa; relief shown by hachures. Text on verso: South and Central Africa. From: Rand, McNally & Co's indexed atlas of the world. Chicago, New York : Rand McNally & Co., [1902?]
